name: #3 The edge of the administratively possible
description: One day I walked towards the Russian border, the edge of where my papers would allow  me to go. The border is the ridge. The bottom left house the last inhabited place before the border.  The music was inspired on the picture, composed while I was there. The visuals were inspired on the music, overdubbed on the picture. They are dynamic clojure(quil) patches, live coded in conjunction with live patched modular music.
